\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個其實係一個音樂節，類似clockenflag，但夜晚嘅時候就會交返個台比主辦HOCC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&lt;on the pulse of hocc 2018 live&gt;<br />\n21-26/12  8:15pm 科學園大廣場(戶外舞台)<br />\nticket $780 <br />\n<br />\n咁佢亦有邀請啲indie band同埋獨立歌手黎一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n&lt;on the pulse of music festival&gt; <br />\n22-23,25-26/12   1-6pm <br />\n<br />\n呢班人其實係有分acoustic set 同埋main stage嘅<br />\nacoustic set就唔會上台表演，會喺附近嘅空地 即係好似busking咁，詳細表演單位可以睇 onthepulseof 嘅ig (acoustic set唔係台上表演，好似都係免費嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n而周國賢就係main stage嘅(即係會上台表演)，佢係喺12月22號出場，至於幾點就...(佢應該係壓軸嘉賓黎嘅，可能會晏小小出場囉) 不過都既然買咗飛，可以早小小入場欣賞埋其他歌手嘅演出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmain stage票價:<br />\n兩日套票(a.22-23/12 or b.25-26/12 日期set死咗嘅，即係冇得22搭26)：$420 (非學生票) //$300 (學生票)<br />\n單日票：$280 (非學生票) //$200 (學生票)<br />\n<br />\n除咗音樂部份，仲有一個叫&lt;on the pulse of christmas market&gt; 22-26/12 1-8pm (*24/12 4-8pm) 科學園一樓平台<br />\n邀請咗接近80個小店黎科學園擺booth，有野食(可以食住野睇show<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) 又有野買，進入呢個市集係免費架 free entrance<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n***一切資料以onthepulseof ig為準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2d9d9c20ab7adbd32642de7164e5341279bea4","tid":903000,"uid":176114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:29:51.000Z","msg":"周國賢未加上去，但已經confirm咗22號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sTvRBcC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsTvRBcC.jpg&h=b99590a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wo11Yrf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?